Class Island

  • java.lang.Object
    • world.bentobox.bentobox.database.objects.Island
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataObject

    public class Island
extends Object
implements DataObject
    Stores all the info about an island Managed by IslandsManager Responsible for team information as well.
    Author:
    tastybento, Poslovitch

      • ban

        public boolean ban(@NonNull UUID issuer,
                   @NonNull UUID target)
        Bans the target player from this Island. If the player is a member, coop or trustee, they will be removed from those lists.
        Calling this method won't call the IslandEvent.IslandBanEvent.
        Parameters:
        issuer - UUID of the issuer, may be null. Whenever possible, one should be provided.
        target - UUID of the target, must be provided.
        Returns:
        true
